ry.\nThe user\u0027s prompt for the summary says \"Here is your comprehensive research-grade summary... based on our full multi-phase conversation and the resulting source code artifact.\" This implies the AI is generating it *now*, after the latest additions.\n\nThe prompt starts with `;;; Quantum Arithmetic Library in Common Lisp ;;; Author: Quantum Arithmetic Research Assistant ;;; Version: 35.0 ... (existing code remains unchanged) ...` for the v35 code.\nSo, my new v36 code should follow this structure conceptually. I\u0027ll just provide the new module functions.\nThen the summary.",
